news.title: Structural assessment report by arrested professor termed Chintels Paradiso building unfit
news.para: In the detailed assessment report with pictures of the building and its map, the professor had said that the Ultrasonic Pulse Velocity (UPV) Test results of the Chintels Paradisco apartment building and other results were doubtful.

news.title: Sub-registrar among five booked for illegal registry of land in Gurugram
news.para: Sources said the registry of the land in Kadipur had been executed on the basis of a fake general power of attorney (GPA) and forged documents and signatures of the original landowner.

news.title: Indore: Drive to recover land diversion tax intensified
news.para: According to SDM Pratul Sinha, the tehsil office has put as many as three properties including that around 8 lakh square feet land of Samriddhi Park Colony, 10.648 hectare land of Vishal Agrotech India Limited and a property of Gyan Vigyan Krida Sansthan on sell through auction on March 26-28 for recovery of close to Rs 1 Crore of land diversion tax due on said immovable assets.
